Generate visual documentation of all app screens.

**Usage**: `/screenshot-catalog [options]`

**Examples**:
- `/screenshot-catalog` - Full app catalog
- `/screenshot-catalog --section=auth` - Catalog auth screens only
- `/screenshot-catalog --states=all` - Include empty/error/loading states

